    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior has noticeable tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. It currently runs but is not reliable for daily use without immediate repairs to the transmission and suspension. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or a source for parts.",
