    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for a buyer who prioritizes function over perfection. The exterior shows visible signs of age, including several noticeable scratches and a few small dings on the passenger side panels. Inside, the upholstery is intact but displays some wear and minor staining consistent with regular use. Mechanically, it runs well, though it has some minor oil seepage and the suspension is beginning to feel its age. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road, provided you don't mind a bit of cosmetic and mechanical character.",
      "price": 23000.0,
