    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a standard of meticulous maintenance that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, this vehicle offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
