      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment and driven only on fair-weather days. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the original alloy wheels are pristine. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no creasing, the carpets are spotless, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. All technological features, including the premium sound system and climate control, operate with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a comprehensive, documented service history from certified technicians. This is a rare, investment-grade example that offers the experience of buying a brand-new vehicle from a previous era. No compromises, no excuses\u2014just pure, unadulterated quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
